Package uk.co.caprica.vlcj.mrl

Provides a set of classes implementing a fluent API for creating properly formatted so-called "Media Resource Locators".

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Mrl
    Specification for a media resource locator.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseDvdMrl
    Base implementation of a media resource locator for DVD MRLs.
    CdMrl
    Implementation of a media resource locator for Audio CDs.
    DvdMrl
    Implementation of a media resource locator for DVDs with menus.
    FileMrl
    Implementation for a file MRL.
    FtpMrl
    Implementation of an HTTP media resource locator.
    HttpMrl
    Implementation of an HTTP media resource locator.
    MmsMrl
    Implementation of an MMS media resource locator.
    RtpMrl
    Implementation of a media resource locator for RTP streams.
    RtspMrl
    Implementation of an HTTP media resource locator.
    SimpleDvdMrl
    Implementation of a media resource locator for DVDs without menus.
    SsmMrl
    Implementation of a media resource locator for SSM streams.
    UdpMrl Deprecated
    UrlMrl
    Implementation for a web-style MRL.
    VcdMrl
    Implementation of a media resource locator for Video CDs.

Package uk.co.caprica.vlcj.mrl Description

Provides a set of classes implementing a fluent API for creating properly formatted so-called "Media Resource Locators".
